        "id": "491a08c1",
        "title": " Rubio 將出庭作證：前室友被控暗中為委內瑞拉行賄",
        "url": "https://www.usnews.com/news/best-states/florida/articles/2026-03-23/rubio-to-testify-in-trial-of-former-roommate-accused-of-secretly-lobbying-for-venezuela",
